overview: They had saved up for their long-awaited traditional trip to Thailand with its beautiful beaches, spicy food, full moon parties, buckets and fire shows. Then came covid-19 and shattered their dreams. However, instead of giving up, they go on a road trip in a rented RV and create their own Koh Phangan in the Swedish forests.
title: Mysko Disko: Ting Tong Trip
